  "title": "CUSTOMER SERVICE EXECUTIVE",
  "description": "<p>Job Description & Requirements</p><p>You will be the voice and face of our company, bridging operations and clients to ensure every order, delivery and request runs seamlessly.<br /><br />Key Responsibilities:<br /><br />Handle customer enquiries via communication channels such as phone, email and WhatsApp in a professional and timely manner;<br />Coordinate laundry pickup and delivery schedules with operations and logistics teams;<br />Prepare service quotations, delivery orders and billing documents;<br />Maintain accurate records of customer transactions and service feedback;<br />Follow up proactively on service issues, customer complaints and resolution tracking;<br />Build positive, long-term relationships with clients to enhance customer satisfaction and loyalty.<br /><br />What We are Looking For:<br /><br />Minimum GCE ‘O’ Level/Diploma in Business, Hospitality or equivalent<br />At least 1–2 years of experience in customer service /client coordination<br />Strong communication and interpersonal skills<br />Proactive, resourceful and customer-oriented with good problem-solving attitude<br />Comfortable using Microsoft Office, data entry and basic ERP/CRM systems</p>",
